    "text": "Help Independent Tracks Succeed Act or the HITS Act\n\nThis bill permits taxpayers to treat as currently deductible expenses the cost of qualified sound recording productions not exceeding $150,000 in a taxable year. The bill defines qualified sound recording production as certain sound recordings produced and recorded in the United States."
